<!DOCTYPE html>
<html ng-app="rbac-forum">
    <head>
        <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1q8mTJOASx8j1Au+a5WDVnPi2lkFfwwEAa8hDDdjZlpLegxhjVME1fgjWPGmkzs7" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.6.1/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-hQpvDQiCJaD2H465dQfA717v7lu5qHWtDbWNPvaTJ0ID5xnPUlVXnKzq7b8YUkbN" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <title> functional forum</title>  
         <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/angular.js/1.5.5/angular.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/angular.js/1.5.5/angular-route.min.js"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
    <div class="container" style="margin-top: 35px">
    
    <div class="page-header page-heading">
        <h1 class="pull-left"> Forum</h1>
        <ol class="breadcrumb pull-right where-am-i">
            <li id = "user"><%= user.local.username %></li>
            <li ng-show='username'><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
            <li class="active"><a href = "profile#/">List of topics</a></li>
            <li ng-hide='username'><a href="/logout" class="btn btn-warning btn-sm">Logout</a></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
    </div>
    <p class="lead">Three roles: moderator, users and guests. Moderators are pre-registered and they can create, modify or delete forum topics and comments. They can also delete registered users if they notice bad behaviour. Users can register to the application and they can create new topics and send comments to any topics. Guests are non-registered users who can only list the topics and the existing comments but they cannot post comments.
        .</p>
     <div ng-view>
         
     </div>
